CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 4, 1941, pg. 24 reads: "Honored At Reception - Miss Pauline Saunders [and] Mrs.Ronald Robinson [were] honored recently at a reception last Saturday evening [given by] her father and sister Jane Saunders and Mrs. George Galway, at the family residence [on] Finance Street. Mrs. Robinson [is] a student at the Pittsburgh Musical Institute - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Pauline Saunders wearing light colored gown with quilted waistband, posed, in the Saunders home on Finance Street
